title: Warriors-Rockets, Celtics, Browns, and top tier players
itunes:title: Warriors-Rockets, Celtics, Browns, and top tier players
description:
Colin explains why the Golden State Warriors should feel good after losing back to back games to the Houston Rockets, the problems with the Boston Celtics and that he was wrong, the Cleveland Browns continuing to be unrealistic, and his top tier NBA players of all-time. Guests include Doug Gottlieb, Chris Broussard, Greg Jennings, and Ric Bucher.
